{
  "text": "It is notable that similar peak circulations were achieved with different combinations of injection time and maximum velocity. It is relevant to the current study to relate the peak strength of the streamwise vortices to injection conditions. Gharib et al. [CITATION_1] found that circular ring vortices had a limiting circulation that was related to the formation time. The equivalent formation time for the slot used in this study when considering the streamwise vortex pair is",
